SELECT COUNT(student_id) AS All_Rounder_Count FROM Student_Performance_Dataset WHERE math_score > 80 AND science_score > 80 AND english_score > 80;
SELECT gender, AVG(final_percentage) AS avg_final_percentage FROM Student_Performance_Dataset WHERE parental_education = "Postgraduate" AND gender = "Female" OR gender = "Male" GROUP BY gender;
SELECT AVG(age) AS average_age, AVG(study_hours_per_day) AS average_study_hours_per_day, AVG(attendance_percentage) AS average_attendance, parental_education FROM Student_Performance_Dataset WHERE performance_level = "Excellent" GROUP BY parental_education ORDER BY parental_education;
